{"thig13.4:0.1":"Therigatha 13.4 ","thig13.4:0.2":"Visatinipata ","thig13.4:0.3":"Sundaritherigatha ","thig13.4:1.1":"“Petani bhoti puttani, ","thig13.4:1.2":"khadamana tuvam pure; ","thig13.4:1.3":"Tuvam diva ca ratto ca, ","thig13.4:1.4":"ativa paritappasi. ","thig13.4:2.1":"Sajja sabbani khaditva, ","thig13.4:2.2":"sataputtani brahmani; ","thig13.4:2.3":"Vasetthi kena vannena, ","thig13.4:2.4":"na balham paritappasi”. ","thig13.4:3.1":"“Bahuni puttasatani, ","thig13.4:3.2":"natisanghasatani ca; ","thig13.4:3.3":"Khaditani atitamse, ","thig13.4:3.4":"mama tuyhanca brahmana. ","thig13.4:4.1":"Saham nissaranam natva, ","thig13.4:4.2":"jatiya maranassa ca; ","thig13.4:4.3":"Na socami na rodami, ","thig13.4:4.4":"na capi paritappayim”. ","thig13.4:5.1":"“Abbhutam vata vasetthi, ","thig13.4:5.2":"vacam bhasasi edisim; ","thig13.4:5.3":"Kassa tvam dhammamannaya, ","thig13.4:5.4":"giram bhasasi edisim”. ","thig13.4:6.1":"“Esa brahmana sambuddho, ","thig13.4:6.2":"nagaram mithilam pati; ","thig13.4:6.3":"Sabbadukkhappahanaya, ","thig13.4:6.4":"dhammam desesi paninam. ","thig13.4:7.1":"Tassa brahme arahato, ","thig13.4:7.2":"dhammam sutva nirupadhim; ","thig13.4:7.3":"Tattha vinnatasaddhamma, ","thig13.4:7.4":"puttasokam byapanudim”. ","thig13.4:8.1":"“So ahampi gamissami, ","thig13.4:8.2":"nagaram mithilam pati; ","thig13.4:8.3":"Appeva mam so bhagava, ","thig13.4:8.4":"sabbadukkha pamocaye”. ","thig13.4:9.1":"Addasa brahmano buddham, ","thig13.4:9.2":"vippamuttam nirupadhim; ","thig13.4:9.3":"Svassa dhammamadesesi, ","thig13.4:9.4":"muni dukkhassa paragu. ","thig13.4:10.1":"Dukkham dukkhasamuppadam, ","thig13.4:10.2":"dukkhassa ca atikkamam; ","thig13.4:10.3":"Ariyam catthangikam maggam, ","thig13.4:10.4":"dukkhupasamagaminam. ","thig13.4:11.1":"Tattha vinnatasaddhammo, ","thig13.4:11.2":"pabbajjam samarocayi; ","thig13.4:11.3":"Sujato tihi rattihi, ","thig13.4:11.4":"tisso vijja aphassayi. ","thig13.4:12.1":"“Ehi sarathi gacchahi, ","thig13.4:12.2":"ratham niyyadayahimam; ","thig13.4:12.3":"Arogyam brahmanim vajja, ","thig13.4:12.4":"‘pabbaji dani brahmano; ","thig13.4:12.5":"Sujato tihi rattihi, ","thig13.4:12.6":"tisso vijja aphassayi’”. ","thig13.4:13.1":"Tato ca rathamadaya, ","thig13.4:13.2":"sahassancapi sarathi; ","thig13.4:13.3":"Arogyam brahmanimvoca, ","thig13.4:13.4":"“pabbaji dani brahmano; ","thig13.4:13.5":"Sujato tihi rattihi, ","thig13.4:13.6":"tisso vijja aphassayi”. ","thig13.4:14.1":"“Etancaham assaratham, ","thig13.4:14.2":"sahassancapi sarathi; ","thig13.4:14.3":"Tevijjam brahmanam sutva, ","thig13.4:14.4":"punnapattam dadami te”. ","thig13.4:15.1":"“Tuyheva hotvassaratho, ","thig13.4:15.2":"sahassancapi brahmani; ","thig13.4:15.3":"Ahampi pabbajissami, ","thig13.4:15.4":"varapannassa santike”. ","thig13.4:16.1":"“Hatthi gavassam manikundalanca, ","thig13.4:16.2":"Phitancimam gahavibhavam pahaya; ","thig13.4:16.3":"Pita pabbajito tuyham, ","thig13.4:16.4":"Bhunja bhogani sundari; ","thig13.4:16.5":"Tuvam dayadika kule”. ","thig13.4:17.1":"“Hatthi gavassam manikundalanca, ","thig13.4:17.2":"Rammam cimam gahavibhavam pahaya; ","thig13.4:17.3":"Pita pabbajito mayham, ","thig13.4:17.4":"Puttasokena attito; ","thig13.4:17.5":"Ahampi pabbajissami, ","thig13.4:17.6":"Bhatusokena attita”. ","thig13.4:18.1":"“So te ijjhatu sankappo, ","thig13.4:18.2":"yam tvam patthesi sundari; ","thig13.4:18.3":"Uttitthapindo uncho ca, ","thig13.4:18.4":"pamsukulanca civaram; ","thig13.4:18.5":"Etani abhisambhonti, ","thig13.4:18.6":"paraloke anasava”. ","thig13.4:19.1":"“Sikkhamanaya me ayye, ","thig13.4:19.2":"dibbacakkhu visodhitam; ","thig13.4:19.3":"Pubbenivasam janami, ","thig13.4:19.4":"yattha me vusitam pure. ","thig13.4:20.1":"Tuvam nissaya kalyani, ","thig13.4:20.2":"theri sanghassa sobhane; ","thig13.4:20.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thig13.4:20.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thig13.4:21.1":"Anujanahi me ayye, ","thig13.4:21.2":"icche savatthi gantave; ","thig13.4:21.3":"Sihanadam nadissami, ","thig13.4:21.4":"buddhasetthassa santike”. ","thig13.4:22.1":"“Passa sundari sattharam, ","thig13.4:22.2":"hemavannam harittacam; ","thig13.4:22.3":"Adantanam dametaram, ","thig13.4:22.4":"sambuddhamakutobhayam”. ","thig13.4:23.1":"“Passa sundarimayantim, ","thig13.4:23.2":"vippamuttam nirupadhim; ","thig13.4:23.3":"Vitaragam visamyuttam, ","thig13.4:23.4":"katakiccamanasavam. ","thig13.4:24.1":"Baranasito nikkhamma, ","thig13.4:24.2":"tava santikamagata; ","thig13.4:24.3":"Savika te mahavira, ","thig13.4:24.4":"pade vandati sundari. ","thig13.4:25.1":"Tuvam buddho tuvam sattha, ","thig13.4:25.2":"tuyham dhitamhi brahmana; ","thig13.4:25.3":"Orasa mukhato jata, ","thig13.4:25.4":"katakicca anasava”. ","thig13.4:26.1":"“Tassa te svagatam bhadde, ","thig13.4:26.2":"tato te aduragatam; ","thig13.4:26.3":"Evanhi danta ayanti, ","thig13.4:26.4":"satthu padani vandika; ","thig13.4:26.5":"Vitaraga visamyutta, ","thig13.4:26.6":"katakicca anasava”. ","thig13.4:27.1":"… Sundari theri …. "}